  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n      \t\t\t\t\t\u003cul\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cli id=\"Entry1\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cspan\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003ca name=\"entry\" id=\"EntryAnchor\"\u003eanchor\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/42/4245b734dcf1540685592d58867a196c.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\" title=\"Poster courtesy of adamymotherthearchitect.com\" data-size=\"2300x3221\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cimg srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/42/4245b734dcf1540685592d58867a196c.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/42/4245b734dcf1540685592d58867a196c.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/42/4245b734dcf1540685592d58867a196c.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\" src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/42/4245b734dcf1540685592d58867a196c.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" title=\"Poster courtesy of adamymotherthearchitect.com\" alt=\"Poster courtesy of adamymotherthearchitect.com\" width=\"514\" height=\"\"/\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ePoster courtesy of adamymotherthearchitect.com\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003eIf you’re in the \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/news/tag/12384/new-york-city\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eNew York City\u003c/a\u003e area on Friday, May 9th, be sure not to miss the premiere of Yael Melamede‘s new documentary \u003cem\u003eADA: My Mother The Architect\u003c/em\u003e depicting the life of the late Ada Karmi-Melamede at the Angelika Film Center. \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eKarmi-Melamede’s work in Israel and New York, where she was denied tenure at the \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/columbiagsapp\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eColumbia GSAPP\u003c/a\u003e in the 1980s. It joins a \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/news/article/150447783/two-new-documentaries-shed-light-on-the-life-of-children-of-star-architects-at-the-architecture-and-design-film-festival\" target=\"_blank\"\u003estring of documentaries\u003c/a\u003e produced by Jim Venturi, \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/news/tag/1029841/nathaniel-kahn\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eNathaniel Kahn\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/news/article/149970749/one-to-one-39-with-tomas-koolhaas-filmmaker-and-son-of-rem\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eTomas Koolhaas\u003c/a\u003e, and other children of famous architects, offering a glimpse into Karmi-Melamede’s career while it \u0026#34;raises timely questions about the cost of success and the legacy we leave behind.\u0026#34;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eA second screening will take place at the Laemmle Royal in Los Angeles on May 16th for West Coast viewers.\u003c/p\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003ciframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/kXet3fS85kk\" width=\"514\" height=\"422\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"\u003e\u003c/iframe\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003eVideo courtesy Salty Features\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003cbr clear=\"all\"/\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\u003ch2\u003eSimilar articles on Archinect that may interest you...\u003c/h2\u003e\n\t\t\u003cul\u0